{"tid":1030291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AV女優Marsha May同14歲以下兒童開群交派對比人拉左","createTime":"2019-02-21T00:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T16:12:53.000Z","uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d08058a497a2fe814e8c6f9029f6ce77cdccf21b","tid":1030291,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:15:40.000Z","msg":"美國21歲AV女優賓德羅絲(Bianca Byndloss)，因涉嫌帶3名未成年少女開雜交趴，而遭到逮捕，她的清純素顏照也跟著曝光。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，案情指出，賓德羅絲被控在前年帶著3名分別為12、13、14歲的少女，與2名18歲男子，一起開雜交趴。賓德羅絲也讓少女們喝伏特加、嗑藥阿普唑侖(Xanax)。據少女們說法，現場就是「大家做愛來做愛去，射來射去」，還用手機拍下雜交過程。賓德羅絲被逮後，遭控猥褻兒童、對兒童進行性行為等罪。<br />\n<br />\n該案在本月初進行宣判，賓德羅絲雖然不用被關，但要繳交罰金754美元(約新台幣23000元)以及緩刑10年。涉案的2名男子在今年稍早，也已被判緩刑10年。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"2814780f1acf3aa62e5603ae935a5533599ccc52","tid":1030291,"uid":70538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:17:47.000Z","msg":"相？"},{"pid":"fbc76254286c14fa25cac7e9a0b4a912f4c3ce68","tid":1030291,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:18:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-4056772/Porn-star-foot-fetishist-21-pleads-guilty-child-abuse-role-drug-vodka-fueled-orgy-three-girls-14-filmed-having-sex-posted-online.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-4056772%2FPorn-star-foot-fetishist-21-pleads-guilty-child-abuse-role-drug-vodka-fueled-orgy-three-girls-14-filmed-having-sex-posted-online.html&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFeDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=47eba3da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-4056772/Porn-star-foot-fetishist-21-pleads-guilty-child-abuse-role-drug-vodka-fueled-orgy-three-girls-14-filmed-having-sex-posted-online.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2016/12/21/22/3B91058300000578-4056772-image-a-125_1482360296175.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2016%2F12%2F21%2F22%2F3B91058300000578-4056772-image-a-125_1482360296175.jpg&h=6f674665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nA porn star who fed three underage girls alcohol and drugs before filming them as they took part in a sex party has been spared jail.<br />\n<br />\nBianca Byndloss, who also goes by Marsha May and Bibi Miami, admitted felony charges of child abuse for her role in the 2014 incident.<br />\n<br />\nThe 21-year-old drove three girls aged 12, 13, and 14 to a house to have sex with her and two of her male friends in Miami in May 2014 and filmed the tryst.<br />\n<br />\nShe later posted photographs and videos of it on Instagram.<br />\n<br />\nAt a December 1 court hearing, Byndloss accepted she had committed felony child abuse.<br />\n<br />\nShe was sentenced to 10 years probation but avoided jail."},{"pid":"ba4d60e6c7d30f3d18a3acf7b0635922160caaa2","tid":1030291,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:18:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b461b1a043a405c9e516a65630c8fae93d48198","tid":1030291,"uid":24007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:18:49.000Z","msg":"有講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2a649f4a69fc442b2b03a69d8505b6e4a79462","tid":1030291,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:20:09.000Z","msg":"Not bad wor"},{"pid":"4d07899c5b5288cbdbe73a31c05f8742777b07e4","tid":1030291,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:20:12.000Z","msg":"正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52ce1cc1d2df1df1523e69695b21adc11b9c62f","tid":1030291,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:30:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.miamiherald.com/news/local/community/miami-dade/article1967360.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.miamiherald